  "tcmTraditionalUsage": {
    "en": "Shengma is acrid, sweet and cooling, affecting the lung, spleen, stomach and large intestine meridians. It is used to release the exterior, clear heat and to raise the yang chi. It helps drive out heat toxins, addressing symptoms such as swollen, painful gums and mouth, oral ulcers and toothache. It can also treat problems associated with yang or chi deficiency such as prolapsed organs, shortness of breath, fatigue and bleeding.\n",
    "zh-Hant": "升麻是常用的發散風熱藥，藥味辛、甘，藥性微寒，歸肺、脾、胃、大腸經，能清熱解毒、發表透疹；又能升舉陽氣，常用於氣虛下陷所致的器官下垂、崩漏下血等，常與黨蔘、黃蓍等中藥同用。\n",
    "zh-Hans": "升麻是常用的發散風热药，药味辛、甘，药性微寒，歸肺、脾、胃、大肠经，能清热解毒、發表透疹；又能升舉阳气，常用于气虚下陷所致的器官下垂、崩漏下血等，常与黨参、黃蓍等中药同用。\n"
  },
